      "title": "Express (b+c) in terms of b",
      "content": "From $b = 0.83c$, we get $c = b/0.83$. Therefore:<br/>$$b + c = b + \\frac{b}{0.83} = b\\left(1 + \\frac{1}{0.83}\\right) = b\\left(\\frac{1.83}{0.83}\\right)$$"
